</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="146" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,1148,1352]" pageId="1" pageNumber="146">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,314,1292,1317]" pageId="1" pageNumber="146">Diagnosis</emphasis>
. Based on hind (?) wing venation only, wing shorter than that of 
<taxonomicName box="[1085,1338,1292,1316]" class="Insecta" family="Anthracoptilidae" genus="Afrocladus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Protorthoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="146" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kenyaensis">
<emphasis box="[1085,1338,1292,1316]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="146">Afrocladus kenyaensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1356,1390,1293,1316]" name="Poland" pageId="1" pageNumber="146">RP</collectingCountry>
not closely parallel to RA near its base, CuA with only three anterior branches instead of four in 
<taxonomicName box="[1180,1429,1328,1352]" class="Insecta" family="Anthracoptilidae" genus="Afrocladus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Protorthoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="146" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kenyaensis">
<emphasis box="[1180,1429,1328,1352]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="146">Afrocladus kenyaensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
